resources.string: "Lolu hlelo ludizayinelwe ukuthi lufanele zonke izingane."
"Lolu hlelo ludizayinelwe izingane ezineminyaka yobudala engu-7 nangaphezulu."
"Abazali abaningi bangathola lolu hlelo lufanele yonke iminyaka."
"Lolu hlelo luqukethe okubalulekile okungatholwa abazali kungafanele izingane ezincane. Iningi labazali lingafuna ukukubuka nezingane zabo ezincane."
"Lolu hlelo luqukethe okunye okubalulekile iningi labazali elingakuthola lungazifanele izingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka yobudala engu-14."
"Lolu hlelo ludizayinelwe ngokuqondile ukuthi libukwe abantu abadala futhi kungenzeka lungazifaneli izingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka engu-17."
"Izethameli ezijwayelekile. Akukho okuzophatha kabi abazali ngokubukwa kwezingane."
"Kuphakanyiswe ukuqondiswa komzali. Kungaqukatha okunye okubalulekile abazali okungeke bakuthandele izingane zabo ezincane."
"Abazali baxwayiswa kakhulu. Okunye okubalulekile kungenzeka kungafaneli abasayoba yintsha."
"Kukhawulelwe, kuqukethe okunye okubalulekile kwabantu abadala. Abazali bayakhuthazwa ukuthi bafunde kabanzi mayelana nefilimu ngaphambi kokuvumela izingane zabo zilibuke nabo."
"Akekho ongaphansi kokungu-17 nongaphansi owamukelwe. Okwabadala ngokusobala. Izingane azamukelwa."
